<TITLE> FBI, Justice Dept to make announcement on mortgages </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 WASHINGTON Thu Jun 19, (bdnews24.com/Reuters) - FBI Director Robert Mueller and Deputy Attorney General Mark Filip will hold a news conference on Thursday at 1:15 p.m. to make an announcement regarding mortgage fraud, the US justice department said on Thursday. It gave no details on the subject, but the announcement comes amid expectations two former hedge fund managers at Bear Stearns are to be indicted on charges connected with mortgage fraud investigations
